title: Handshake Medium Light Skin Tone
alsoKnownAs: Shaking Hands Medium Light Skin Tone
description: Represents agreement, partnership, or a friendly greeting between two people, specifically with a medium-light skin tone.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the handshake emoji with a medium-light skin tone depicts two hands clasped in a firm yet welcoming gesture, showcasing Apple's signature smooth textures and realistic lighting. The rounded fingers and subtle shading give it a tactile and professional appearance, symbolizing agreement, collaboration, and trust. This emoji is a clear visual representation of unity and partnership in communication on Apple devices.
